video.title: Q&A (with Jayasara and Jitindriya and whoever wants to attend 😎 😻 )
video.description:
Greetings all - the Q&A livestream will be held this Thursday, June 3rd at 1pm AEST (Sydney, Australia time). 
Please note, it's Wednesday evening in the States and early morning in the UK and other parts of Europe, and parts of SE Asia.

For conversion for your part of the world, please see here:
https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/converter.html
